    "dj_piggy": {
      "subtitle": "Booth on fire",
      "lead": "The mental and social monster. Less body, more head. Cheerful chaos, high energy, constant motion.",
      "block_title": "The lift",
      "p1": "The party starts in your head.",
      "p2": "Ideas, laughter, chaos… everything spikes at once.",
      "p3": "DJ Piggy won't chill you out—it spins you up.",
      "p4": "DJ Piggy wasn't built to stay quiet. It was built to fire up the engine.",
      "p5": "The lift is on the inside: faster thoughts, easy conversation, loose laughter, and a sense of motion. The plant is more open and less compact, with a more complex aroma profile and a less physical hit than its heavier sisters. It doesn't relax the body—it wakes up the head. And if you overdo it, it can speed up more than you'd like.",
      "tagline": "SOCIAL. CEREBRAL. IN MOTION.",
      "spec_lead": "Hybrid with sativa lean. Active, cerebral, great for social or creative moments.",
